
Usage: leshif-wol [-OPTION] [-OPTION] ...
       leshif-wol - m [hardware_address] -i [ip_address] -p [port] -n 81

Otions:
    -v  displays leshif-wol version
    -m  set hardware_address -> required option
    -i  set destination IP address -> default address: net-interface broadcast address
    -p  set destination port -> default port: 9
    -n  set used network interface
    -f  full sending mod (used all net)
    -na displays all network interface
    -nu displays used network interface